119
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:34,564
Kailangan mong gumawa ng isang hakbang.

120
00:06:34,723 --> 00:06:35,871
Kailangan mong patunayan ito.

121
00:06:35,871 --> 00:06:37,937
Tingnan kung mayroon talagang nasa likod

122
