(Salamat.
Sinigurado kong nalabhan itong mabuti)

147
00:08:09,320 --> 00:08:10,080
Salamat.

148
00:08:10,733 --> 00:08:13,029
At salamat ulit sa isang gabi.

149
00:08:14,388 --> 00:08:15,218
Huwag mong banggitin.

150
00:08:16,454 --> 00:08:17,355
Bye.

151
