192
00:12:18,395 --> 00:12:19,155
Mukhang maganda?

193
00:12:20,285 --> 00:12:20,973
Oo naman.

194
00:12:21,538 --> 00:12:23,128
At paano mo kadalasang gusto itong luto?

195
00:12:26,483 --> 00:12:27,560
Hulaan ko...

196
00:12:28,319 --> 00:12:29,149
Katamtaman-bihirang?

197
00:12:31,622 --> 00:12:32,699
Medium-rare ay ayos lang.

198
00:12:34,023 --> 00:12:37,554
Pagkatapos ay kailangan kong maghanap ng alak
na perpektong pares sa ulam na ito.

199
00:12:40,115 --> 00:12:42,217
Okay, hayaan natin ang isang ito.

200
00:12:42,782 --> 00:12:44,124
Ito ay may buong katawan.

201
00:12:44,124 --> 00:12:45,607
Dapat itong sumama nang maayos sa steak.

202
00:12:48,150 --> 00:12:50,092
- Salamat.
- Oo naman, ginoo.

203
00:12:53,871 --> 00:12:56,238
Mukhang expert ka talaga.

204
00:12:56,962 --> 00:12:58,392
Kailangan kong malaman ang isa o dalawa,

205
