May mali ba?

210
00:13:44,852 --> 00:13:46,088
Masyado bang malaki ang pinutol ko?

211
00:13:46,883 --> 00:13:47,483
Hindi.

212
00:13:47,483 --> 00:13:49,796
Ayoko lang ng patatas.

213
00:13:50,242 --> 00:13:51,122
Oh!

214
00:13:51,209 --> 00:13:52,763
Nakuha ko. Hayaan mo akong tulungan ka niyan.

215
